Package: heekscnc
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python-wxgtk2.8, python (>= 2.5), python-area, heekscad (>= 1.0.0)
Enhances: heekscad
Description: CAM add-on for HeeksCAD
 HeeksCNC adds machining features to HeeksCAD.
 .
 Using a 2D (e.g. DXF files) or 3D models, HeeksCNC allow user to create
 machining operations.
 HeeksCNC's post-processing produces G-Code/NC code file which is interpreted
 and displayed in HeeksCAD.
 .
 HeeksCNC features many machining operations like: profile, pocket and drill.
 It also allow user-defined python script as post-process.
